        <item>
            <title>《Mouse》發布遊戲示範影片，波蘭獨立開發 1930s 黑白卡通風格 FPS</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/mouse-from-fumi-game/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mouse-from-fumi-game</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/mouse-from-fumi-game/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 07:50:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mouse]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[獨立遊戲]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210483</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>波蘭獨立遊戲工作室 Fumi Game 開發的復古射擊遊戲《Mouse》日前上傳了早期遊玩示範影片，讓玩家以第一人稱投身 1930 年代黑白卡通世界。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="MOUSE Early Gameplay Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4KoNDAW4JrE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《Mouse》是一款 Noir 黑色風格的 FPS 射擊遊戲，其獨特視覺風格靈感源自 1930 年代的經典卡通，將玩家帶回 20 世紀 30 年代的橡皮管動畫（Rubber Hose Animation）世界。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>遊戲中玩家會扮演出一名私家偵探，在一個充滿幫派、流氓的城市中探索。玩家可以在這個混亂、腐敗和充滿活力的黑色城市中利用各種武器、能量道具和爆炸物追求正義，阻止腐敗的政客繼續掌管這個城市。遊戲的武器非常有玩味，而且生命值顯示非常獨特，配上卡通人物般的敵人，為傳統 FPS 遊戲帶來一抹輕鬆的風景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Fumi Game 在 Steam 表示，《Mouse》預計將於 2025 年發行。</p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4KoNDAW4JrE&amp;ab_channel=FumiGames">Fumi Game@YouTube</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2416450/Mouse/">Steam</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/mouse-from-fumi-game/game-channel/">《Mouse》發布遊戲示範影片，波蘭獨立開發 1930s 黑白卡通風格 FPS</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
