        <item>
            <title>玩家沉迷 Steam Deck 散熱位氣味   Valve：氣體無害但不要再聞</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=steam-deck-smell</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 07:49:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam deck]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Steam Deck OLED]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Valve]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209799</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信許多人都喜歡一些「奇怪」的氣味，例如停車場、油站，甚至是收據的氣味，但近日外國有一名玩家喜歡的氣味就更加「奇怪」，他愛上的是 Steam Deck 散熱排氣口散發的味道，其後更詢問 Valve 官方這樣聞 Steam Deck 是否安全。</p><p>Steam Deck 頂部設有散熱孔，遊玩時內置風扇會轉動，以排出熱氣，幫助 Steam Deck 散熱。有部分玩家似乎開發了奇怪的癖好，遊玩時刻意將鼻子貼近排氣口，盡情享受 Steam Deck 的獨有味道。</p><p>由於電子產品內部零件甚多，因此無法確定這些零件運作時溫度升高後會否產生對人體有害的物質，所以 Reddit 一名玩家 <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Metapod100/">@Metapod100</a> 專誠向 Valve 查詢，到底「吸 Steam Deck」 是否安全。Valve 官方回應指， Steam Deck 正常運作時排放的氣體沒有安全問題，但仍不建議玩家主動吸入電子設備排出的氣體。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1.jpeg 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-710x1536.jpeg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamDeck/comments/18grijh/i_asked_valve_about_sniffing_the_vent_and/?rdt=48448">Reddit</a></p><p>除了 @Metapod100 外，外國也有不少玩家表示喜歡 Steam Deck 散熱口排出的味道。X（前稱 Twitter）上就有網友 @SirLarr 表示他聞過 Steam Deck 的味道後發覺非常好聞。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I just huffed the new electronics fumes directly from the Steam Deck&#39;s vent.</p><p>That&#39;s goooood shiiiiiitttttt</p><p>&mdash; Lawrence Sonntag (@SirLarr) <a href="https://twitter.com/SirLarr/status/1539396062628020225?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 21, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>除此之外， Reddit 上亦有網友 @oxelhare 表示他已經 44 歲了，但每次聞到 Steam Deck 排氣口的味道時也會覺得自己像是回到 12 歲般樣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-132917-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-132917-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-132917-768x501.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-132917.jpg 823w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamDeck/comments/14bkhr8/comment/joh69ka/">Reddit</a></p><p>廠商永遠不可以低估遊戲玩家的「創意」。早前 Nintendo 推出 Switch 之時，為了避免兒童誤吞 Switch 遊戲卡帶，Nintendo 刻意在卡帶塗上世界上已知最苦的化合物：苯甲地那銨。這種苦味劑的苦度會苦到令人產生陰影。據 Yahoo 新聞報道指，如果奎寧的苦度是 1 的話，苯甲地那銨的苦度達 1000。儘管如此，仍然有不少玩家會刻意嚐試 Switch 卡帶。</p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://kotaku.com/valve-steam-deck-fumes-vent-smell-good-safe-exhaust-1851094071">kotaku</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=260674">巴哈姆特</a>、<a href="https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/61589/valve-ask-not-to-huffing-steam-deck-vent-fume">4Gamers</a>、<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/switch%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E7%89%87%E6%9C%83%E8%8B%A6-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A1%97%E4%BA%86%E9%80%99%E6%9D%B1%E8%A5%BF-104557587.html">Yahoo 新聞</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/">玩家沉迷 Steam Deck 散熱位氣味   Valve：氣體無害但不要再聞</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《Call of Duty》官方制裁外掛玩家，多人模式一用這把槍即死</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 07:48:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Call of Duty]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210561</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小編閒時很喜歡玩多人遊戲，但如果場內有外掛玩家的話，會嚴重影響到遊戲體驗。最近《Call of Duty Modern Warfare 3》多人遊戲模式出現大批外掛玩家，拿着本來只供 DMZ 模式使用的雷射槍周圍胡作非為，嚴重破壞守法玩家的遊戲體驗。官方昨日（13 日）宣佈，以後在多人遊戲模式使用雷射槍的玩家一開槍就會「被自殺」。</p><p>《Call of Duty Modern Warfare 3》玩家 <a href="https://twitter.com/txtyy_">@txtyy_</a>上週在 X（前稱 Twitter）上傳了一段遊戲影片。影片中可見 @txtyy_ 多次被雷射槍「秒殺」，下面有網友亦表示感同身受，並分享相似的經歷。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">silent aim and a raygun, games chalked <a href="https://t.co/jlU4IbZmoF">pic.twitter.com/jlU4IbZmoF</a></p><p>&mdash; ⛧ (@txtyy_) <a href="https://twitter.com/txtyy_/status/1733309656578076892?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 9, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-175924-694x371.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-175924-694x371.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-175924-1280x684.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-175924-768x410.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-175924-1536x820.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-14-175924.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲@txtyy_ 被雷射槍秒殺的場景，圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/txtyy_/status/1733309656578076892">txtyy_@X</a></p><p>雷射槍實際上是 DMZ 模式中出現的武器，本來就不是設計予玩家在多人模式使用。《Call of Duty》官方今晨（13 日）在 X 發文表示由今日起，所有在多人模式中使用雷射槍的外掛玩家，一開槍就會立即「被自殺」。官方發文後很多玩家在下面回應額手稱慶。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://game.udn.com/game/story/122089/7638320">udn</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/">《Call of Duty》官方制裁外掛玩家，多人模式一用這把槍即死</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
